         <abstract>
            <p>Dǝrsāna Rufāʾel is a composition for the feast of Archangel Raphael on the 3rd of Ṗagʷǝmen.
               It consists of a homily by John Chrysostom on Raphael, a collection of miracles and two homilies on the Living Creatures
               (by Rǝtuʿa Haymānot and Chrystostom).
